Join now GPPD the # 1 cutting-edge international partnerships portal to advertise business, joint ventures, franchisee, investors, tenders, projects, jobs, internships and volunteers on the net www.gppd.vacau.com. Business, government, partner find or post tenders, investments, grants- GPPD – the best online business partnerships portal! Global Partnerships Portal for Peace and Development The best business meeting place on the net, to advertise and post for:

  • Business looking for resellers or franchisee in another country;
  • Government organization that have tenders or are looking for international partners;
  • Nonprofit looking for grants, sponsors, volunteers or international projects;
  • Church looking for interfaith or international partners;
  • Sport organization or club looking for sponsors or international partners;
  • Culture organization looking for international partners to cooperate;
  • Science organization or laboratory looking for international partners or projects;
  • Health, Travel, Arts, education etc organizations to partner and network. GPPD - Global Partnerships Portal for Peace and Development is a branch of an incredibly fast-growing international movement, which now boasts all over the world. Please help this group grow by spreading the word! So, why not “pay it forward” and tell 3 (or more) people how wonderful www.GPPD.vacau.com is! You tell your friends, your family, your neighbors, your co-workers…and they tell theirs, and so on …well, you get the idea!
